From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Apr 2026 17:10:07 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(starry): add real procfs cpuinfo, meminfo, mounts, and
 random uuid

Expose allocator-backed meminfo, arch-specific cpuinfo, multi-line mounts,
loadavg/uptime/version/filesystems stubs, and /proc/sys/kernel/random
uuid (fresh per read) plus stable boot_id for Linux userland probes.

Made-with: Cursor

